main event: A witness reported seeing a yellowish, Saturn-like object that hovered and then disappeared into the sky on August 13, 1965.
interesting points: The object was described as stationary and yellowish in color., The witness estimated the speed of the object to be between 1200-3500 F.P.S., The observation lasted approximately 5 minutes., The witness indicated the object appeared to be very high in the sky., The witness was 17 years old and had an interest in UFOs as a social worker.
